8 An Act relating to elections; amending 26 O.S. 2021,
Section 14-105, as amended by Section 1, Chapter 292,
9 O.S.L. 2022 (26 O.S. Supp. 2024, Section 14-105),
which relates to applications for absentee ballots;
10 requiring statement listing reason why voter cannot
vote in person on election day; directing certain
11 registered voters to indicate date for which they are
requesting an absentee ballot; providing for
12 codification; and providing an effective date.
